archimate:BusinessRole.name: Man-Made Thing
archimate:BusinessRole.documentation: A Thing generated by human activity of some kind. Examples include manufactured goods, houses, cars, books, documents, and digital files. Man-Made Things include both Active Things and Passive Things. Mutually exclusive with Natural Thing. See Appendix B and Appendix C.
